quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  10,21,"Si Men mee…óinirii yim…ďe …ďen yurmeende …ďaawo lorra memnooka …ďe, jaka yoo hi…ďe mari pewje e Aayeeje Amen …óen. Maaku : \"Ko Alla …ďuri yaawude fewjoore\". Pellet, Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďen hino winnda kon ko fewjoton"
  10,22,"Ko kanko woni doginoowo on ka njorndi e ka maayo, haa si on wonii ka laa…óe, …óe doginira …ďe henndu laa…ďndu, …ďe weltora ndu. Ara e majje henndu bippooru, molloo…óe (bempejje) …óen ara e ma…ď…ďe immorde e kala baŇčŇče, …ďe fellita wonnde kam…ďe …ďe hu…ďindaama, …ďe toroo Alla ko …ďe la…ď…ďinana Mo diina kan, […ďe wi'a]: \"Si A da…óndii men e …óum …óoo, pellet, men laatoday e yettoo…ďe [Ma] …ďen"
  10,23,"∆Āaawo nde O da…óndi …ďe, e jaka yoo kam…ďe hi…ďe bewira ko leydi ko adaa e goonga. Ko onon yo yim…ďe, anndee bewre mon nden yantay e wonkiiji mon. Ko dakamme nguurndam aduna. Refti ko ka Amen woni rutorde mon, Men yeetitoo on ko laatino…óon gollayno…óon"
  10,24,"Anndee misal nguurndam aduna …óam, ko wano ndiyam …óam Men jippini immorde ka kammu, pu…ói leydi ndin jillondira e majjam …óum ko yim…ďe e neemoraa…ói √Īaamata. Haa si ndi leydi ndi ∆īettii cu…óaari mayri ndi cu…óike, yim…ďe mayri …ďen jikka wonnde ko …ďe hattam…ďe (so√Īugol) e mayri, yami- roore Amen ardira e mayri jemma maa √Īalorma, Men wa…óa (pu…ói) …óin so√Īaa…ói wa si tawii …ói mo∆ī- ∆īaano hanki mun. Ko wano nii Men fensitirta Aayeeje …óen wonannde yim…ďe miijitotoo…ďe …ďen"
  10,25,"Alla no nodda on faade e galle kisal, Himo fewna on Mo o muyyi faade e laawol focciingol ngol"
  10,26,"Hino woodani …ďen mo∆ī∆īim…ďe (golle) mo∆ī∆īere e …ďeydaari. Nduggu hippataa geece ma…ď…ďe …óen, wanaa kadi koyeera. Ko …ďen woni yim…ďe Aljanna …ďen, kam…ďe ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe ton"
  10,27,"∆Āen faggitii…ďe boneeji …óin, njo…ďdi bone ko yeru makko. Koyeera hippay …ďe, Alanaa …ďe immorde ka Alla hay da…óndoowo, A sikkay geece ma…ď…ďe …óen ko hippiraa ko ta∆īontinnde jemma ni…ď…ďutu…óo. Ko …ďen woni yim…ďe Yiite, kam…ďe ko luttoo…ďe ton"
  10,28,"√Ďalnde Men moo…ďindirta …ďe denndaangal, refti Men wi'ana …ďen sirkunoo…ďe : \"Wonee e nokku mon, onon e kafidii…ďe mon.\" Men senndindira hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, kafidii…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen wi'a : \"Wonaa menen wonuno…óon e rewude"
  10,29,"Alla yonii seedee hakkunde amen e mon. Si ko woni, men laatinoke welsindii…ďe gaay e dewe mon …óen"
  10,30,Ko …óon wonkii kala jarriborte ko ki ardinnoo. ∆Āe ruttitee ka Alla Gi…óo ma…ď…ďe on ka goonga; ko …ďe wonunoo fefindaande kon majjira …ďe